*HEADING
 Single-element verification of umat_klempt_voigt.f (Option A, mode A).
 Same elastic kernel + analytic Jaumann tangent as umat_klempt2025.f.
 Growth via PREDEF(1)=alpha ramped against a clamped face; NLGEOM.
 Confirms the hand-derived consistent tangent gives clean implicit
 convergence in a real Abaqus increment loop (Abaqus = ground truth).
